      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Rear wiper blade removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. Rear wiper blade removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "1019_5.0_jpn_11580904_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Turn the rear wiper blade (A) to unlock it and remove it from the rear wiper arm (B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "1019_5.0_jpn_11580905_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "2",
      "text": "Lift the rubber (A) and pull it out from the rear wiper blade (B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "1019_5.0_jpn_11677570_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "3",
      "text": "Remove the retainer (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "After installation, check that the rear wiper arm operates smoothly."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. Rear wiper blade installation"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "1019_5.0_jpn_11677571_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Install the retainer (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "1019_5.0_jpn_11580906_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "2",
      "text": "Install the rubber (A) to the rear wiper blade (B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "1019_5.0_jpn_11580907_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "3",
      "text": "Install the rear wiper blade (A) onto the rear wiper arm (B)."
    }
  ],
